Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:48.70,*Default1,46,0000,0000,0000,,遠雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.80,*Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}爸爸, 那裡會有熊貓嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.80,*Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.60,*Default5,48,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什麼? 熊貓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.80,*Default5,49,0000,0000,0000,,那麼, 我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.10,*Default5,50,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.10,*Default5,51,0000,0000,0000,,你還在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.90,*Default5,52,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥, 你要是有空至少也洗洗浴室吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.00,*Default5,53,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}她...發現了嗎?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.30,*Default5,54,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}只是一瞬間的事{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.80,*Default5,55,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不可能發現的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.30,*Default5,56,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不可能...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.90,*Default5,57,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.70,*Default5,58,0000,0000,0000,,午餐要吃什麼? 涼麵好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.70,*Default5,59,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.40,*Default5,60,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去剪頭髮還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.20,*Default5,61,0000,0000,0000,,我們就先...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.00,*Default5,62,0000,0000,0000,,妳進過我房間對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.60,*Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,耶!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.60,*Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.60,*Default5,64,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天要倒垃圾, 所以剛剛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.70,*Default5,65,0000,0000,0000,,我之前有跟妳說過對吧? 不要隨便進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,*Default5,66,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 我只是把垃圾桶清乾淨, 其他什麼都沒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.40,*Default5,67,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在那裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.50,*Default5,68,0000,0000,0000,,我的垃圾我自己會處理!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.30,*Default5,69,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不喜歡我隨便進妳房間吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.70,*Default5,70,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.60,*Default5,71,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:08.30,*Default5,72,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋, 妳神經太大條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.00,*Default5,73,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.90,*Default5,74,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想幫忙才這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.70,*Default5,75,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.60,*Default5,76,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讓我說第二遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.70,*Default5,77,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}到底怎麼了?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.90,*Default5,78,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}這是遷怒嗎?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.00,*Default5,79,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不會吧? 不可能...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.00,*Default5,80,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那只是一瞬間的事{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.50,*Default5,81,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}她一定沒注意到才對{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.10,*Default5,82,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}可是...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.90,*Default5,83,0000,0000,0000,,有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.30,*Default5,84,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:24.80,*Default5,85,0000,0000,0000,,絕對有問題, 只不過是進房間而已\N沒必要那麼生氣對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.80,*Default5,86,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有什麼不想被人看見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.60,*Default5,87,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.40,*Default5,88,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.60,*Default5,89,0000,0000,0000,,是禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.30,*Default5,90,0000,0000,0000,,他先故意裝得好像很壞的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.00,*Default5,91,0000,0000,0000,,然後明天就會變成溫柔的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.60,*Default5,92,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 那種作戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.00,*Default5,93,0000,0000,0000,,七夏, 妳明天生日對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:53.50,*Default5,94,0000,0000,0000,,不可能! 不可能! 那是絕對不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.70,*Default5,95,0000,0000,0000,,說不定七夏妳哥哥其實很單純喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.40,*Default5,96,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要擺祈願竹吧...祈願竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.10,*Default5,97,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是七夕相親啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.10,*Default5,98,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}七夕(たなばた) = 牛郎和織女在七月一年一度的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.40,*Default5,99,0000,0000,0000,,對年輕女性會員而言這氣氛很重要吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.40,*Default5,100,0000,0000,0000,,年輕女性會員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.10,*Default5,101,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.10,*Default5,102,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.40,*Default5,103,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 妳做什麼...!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:28.10,*Default5,104,0000,0000,0000,,不過, 不發一語在那邊綁短籤的傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.10,*Default5,105,0000,0000,0000,,看起來也挺噁心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:43.52,*Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H464751&\}{\frz-8\pos(550,600)}我\N想\N要\N妹\N妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:43.52,*Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H464751&\}{\frz-10\pos(420,800)}小\N田\N切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.20,*Default5,107,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 你做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.90,*Default5,108,0000,0000,0000,,有了妹妹可是沒半點好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:56.00,*Default5,109,0000,0000,0000,,一個能夠跟可愛的妹妹搶電視節目看的人\N是不會了解我的心情的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.40,*Default5,110,0000,0000,0000,,真暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.60,*Default5,111,0000,0000,0000,,下起雨可就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.40,*Default5,112,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝一杯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.40,*Default5,113,0000,0000,0000,,好啊! 我正想問你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.80,*Default5,114,0000,0000,0000,,不打電話沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.30,0:09:47.10,*Default5,115,0000,0000,0000,,自從七夏來了以後, 你只要晚回家就會打電話的不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.00,*Default5,116,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.30,*Default5,117,0000,0000,0000,,想裝傻也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.90,*Default5,118,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話, 嘴巴擦乾淨啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.80,*Default5,119,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙要怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:06.70,*Default5,120,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}突然闖入我的生活的, 是她{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.10,0:10:29.40,*Default5,121,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那傢伙的事情, 與我無關{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:48.70,*Default5,122,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那傢伙...真的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.60,*Default5,123,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.10,*Default5,124,0000,0000,0000,,別過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.10,*Default5,125,0000,0000,0000,,碎片很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.90,*Default5,126,0000,0000,0000,,那個...是我的碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:55.70,*Default5,127,0000,0000,0000,,那個碗我很喜歡的! 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.40,*Default5,128,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我明天就沒辦法吃飯了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:30.20,*Default5,129,0000,0000,0000,,那個...哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.30,*Default5,130,0000,0000,0000,,明天是什麼日子你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:42.70,*Default5,131,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要很早出門, 便當不用準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.20,*Default5,132,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}說出來{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.10,*Default5,133,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}對不起我聞了妳的內衣{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.60,*Default5,134,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}對不起我對妳動了邪念{\i0}
