Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.40,*Default5,192,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.00,*Default5,193,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:50.80,*Default5,194,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛! 哥哥昨天晚上好可怕!
